ComicInfo.Summary:
Following up on the dud bomb the Dredd's Apocalypse Squad infiltrate the silo, and Dredd launches all it's missiles at East-Meg One.
Dix-I day offers an amnesty to all deserters, and for Bagman's sake Rogue reports in, and arrives just in time to stop a Filth Columnist saboteur.
